<i>Bioinformatics</i>. 21(12):2927-9. [PMID: <a title="Link to PubMed" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&db=pubmed&dopt=Abstract&list_uids=15817696" target=_blank>15817696</a>]</p>
